flowchart TD
USER[Human Operator / SRE] --> UI[Next.js OpsPilot Dashboard<br/>Vercel Frontend]

```
UI --> API[FastAPI Backend API<br/>Incident and Approval Endpoints]

API --> ORCH[Multi-Agent Incident Orchestrator]

ORCH --> A1[Triage Agent<br/>Severity, impact, blast radius]
ORCH --> A2[Observability Agent<br/>Metrics, logs, deployments]
ORCH --> A3[Runbook Agent<br/>Runbooks and prior incidents]
ORCH --> A4[Hypothesis Agent<br/>Ranked root-cause analysis]
ORCH --> A5[Remediation Planner<br/>Safe action and rollback plan]
ORCH --> A6[Risk & Safety Agent<br/>Policy and approval check]
ORCH --> A7[Approval Agent<br/>Human decision brief]

A7 --> APPROVAL{Human Approval Required?}

APPROVAL -->|Approved| EXEC[Remediation Executor<br/>Controlled action simulation]
APPROVAL -->|Blocked| STOP[Stop / Escalate]

EXEC --> REVIEW[Execution Review Agent<br/>Before and after comparison]
REVIEW --> POST[Postmortem Agent<br/>Root cause and follow-up actions]

ORCH --> AUDIT[Agent Timeline<br/>Audit Trail]
ORCH --> STATE[Incident State Store]

A1 --> QWEN[Qwen Cloud Model API<br/>Real mode after credits]
A2 --> TOOLS[Operational Tools<br/>Metrics, logs, deployment history]
A3 --> KB[Runbook Knowledge Base]
A4 --> QWEN
A5 --> QWEN
A6 --> QWEN
A7 --> QWEN
POST --> QWEN

API -. planned .-> ECS[Alibaba Cloud ECS<br/>Dockerized Backend]
```

